name: Orn Free Taa
Lore: 'Obese Rutian Twi''lek senator. Once a tax collector, he has used his connections and political power to fuel a myriad of devious plots for whomever can make him the highest offer.',
Text: 'Agendas: taxation, wealth. While in a senate majority, once per turn may take your just drawn battle destiny into hand. During opponent''s deploy phase, may use X Force to place Taa in your Used Pile. (X = cards in opponent''s Force Pile.)',
